{"word":"ἄρηξις","slug":"ἄρηξις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄρηξις</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀρήγω'><el>ἀρήγω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>help, succour</i>, <el>τινος</el> <i>from</i> a person, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> rei, <i>help against</i> a thing, <i>means of averting</i> it, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}